data.description: Welcome to a charming home on .90 acre property. It sits in Nine Mile Falls next to grocery and shopping. The home is 3 bed, 2 bath. This property provides a ton of storage with a two car garage and a shop like building behind it with a sauna, shower and space for a gym. Your furry friends will love the large fenced in kennel area complete with a dog house. The garden area with a greenhouse and a orchard feels properly set up with new grass in the backyard. The sprinkler system in the front yard is new within the last year. The property contains 6 cherry trees, 2 plum trees, 3 pear trees and 1 apple tree. The gym equipment can also be purchased.
